Fried Egg Burger

25 min
$12.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Description

A juicy burger topped with a perfectly fried egg, combining savory flavors with a creamy texture.

Ingredients

  • lettuce: 4 leaves
